            </DemoSnippet>

            <p>
                If we inspect the image element in the developer tools, we can see that the <Highlight>src</Highlight> of the image is a 
                <Highlight>temporary BLOB URL</Highlight> as shown below. 
            </p>

            <figure>
                <img src="./image/blogs/blazor/wasm/prevent-image-leech-by-dynamically-streaming-image-in-blazor-wasm/temporary-url.png" alt="temporary url" class="[ w-full ]" />
            </figure>

            <p>
                When you copy that URL and try to access it via browser you get an <Highlight>Error 404 saying that file cannot be accessed</Highlight> 
