            </figure>

            <p>
                As a result, it makes it more <Highlight>difficult to download the image outside the application</Highlight> and 
                <Highlight>prevents unauthorised use</Highlight> of the image.
            </p>

            <h4 id="advantages-of-dynamic-streaming">Advantages of Dynamic Streaming</h4>

            <p>
                The advantages of dynamic streaming are as follows,
            </p>

            <ul>
                <li><Highlight>Unauthorised Image Access</Highlight>.</li>
                <li><Highlight>Bandwidth Savings</Highlight>.</li>
                <li><Highlight>Cost Savings</Highlight>.</li>
            </ul>
        </How>

        <Summary>
            In this article, we learnt about the <Highlight>image leeching problem</Highlight> and how to prevent it by 
            <Highlight>dynamically streaming image</Highlight> in Blazor WASM apps. We also learnt about the advantages of dynamic streaming. 
            Hope you enjoyed reading this article. Thank you for reading from us.
        </Summary>
